# PyInstaller
#  Usually these files are written by a python script, you may want to ignore them
#  Our spec file can be committed if we want to share build configs, but usually builds are ignored
#  Since HangoutPlanner.spec is present in the workspace, we will allow it or ignore build/ and dist/
#  Leaving .spec out of ignore if we want to track it, but adding build/ and dist/ to ignore.

